Problem 8.2

ggplot(CPS85)+
  aes(x=wage, fill=sex)+
  geom_density(adjust = 1L, alpha = 0.5)+
  scale_fill_hue()+
  theme_minimal()+
  facet_wrap(vars(married))

ggplot(CPS85)+
  aes(x=age, y=wage)+
  geom_smooth(aes(color=sex))+
  facet_grid(vars(married))+
  theme(legend.position = "right")
ggplot(CPS85)+
  aes(x=age, y=wage)+
  geom_smooth(aes(color=sex))+
  facet_wrap(vars(sector))+
  theme(legend.position = "right")

Problem 8.3

ggplot(CPS85)+
  aes(x=age, y=wage)+
  geom_point()

ggplot(CPS85)+
  aes(x=age, y=wage, shape=sex)+
  geom_point()+
  theme(legend.position = "top")

ggplot(CPS85)+
  aes(x=age, y=wage, shape=sex)+
  geom_point()+
  facet_grid(vars(married))+
  theme(legend.position = "top")

ggplot(CPS85)+
  aes(x=age, y=wage, shape=married)+
  geom_point()+
